notepad .gitignore
```

Paste this:
```
# Virtual environment
venv/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python

# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.pyproj
*.sln
Debug/
Release/
x64/
x86/

